/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"係所以野都太快<br />\n<br />\n越近光速，時間就變慢道理一樣"},{"pid":"f9b5b9f83d976ce08304857248293be85d877eda","tid":2497721,"uid":63157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"係個層面改變左姐"},{"pid":"16f0afa3d82b5ba3c24ce02c0cc35234a5b08272","tid":2497721,"uid":229607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"其實就算唔講software/網絡上既upgrade, <br />\n3D printing 都算係近幾年既新科技，<br />\n成條橋成間屋都print 到出黎，<br />\n亦成功令簡單既塑膠制品production 可以家用化。<br />\n<br />\n仲有智能家居，十年八年前屋企行Lutron 光暗燈飾已經好先進，<br />\n而家只要你有心，就可以將成間屋智能化，<br />\n網絡控制既門鎖，燈，冷氣，風扇，音響，<br />\n之前Iron Man 裡面先有既野而家有少少錢都可以係屋企做到，<br />\n唔需要再驚唔記得熄冷氣，去左旅行唔記得熄燈，<br />\n或者有速遞或有鐘點要有人係屋企開門等等。<br />\n<br />\n當然智能家居亦帶黎好大既security 同 privacy issue"},{"pid":"f743b2877e1d3adafb0d525f82a12ecaa424a04c","tid":2497721,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0008e0057c6370b3d6063ff36834ab82727b53f","tid":2497721,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbe11b19aa7d5b5bd93dbf19e9e2de223284ec94","tid":2497721,"uid":134774,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"唔覺<br />\n電動車 alpha go crypto currency"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"alpha go 只係將廿幾三十年前嘅發明同理論（convolutional neural network, reinforcement learning）用勁嘅電腦堆砌出嚟，唔算係咩新科技。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"咁你咁講 Dyson sphere 咪係宜家嘅發明來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到整到果陣就話以前一早有啦 係宜家先砌到啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}